<hr local-id=3D"fbf4f06ee821">
<h2 local-id=3D"69178ea3d107" id=3D"bitloopsinit-3.Scope">3. Scope</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"690d9e1f8c31" id=3D"bitloopsinit-Inscope">In scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"8065fa1a4d57">
<li local-id=3D"b74e8624b05e">
<p local-id=3D"8717e8105ef7">CLI arg contract for <code>bitloops init</code=
> (<code>--force</code>, <code>--agent</code>, <code>--telemetry</code>).</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e9a490db4bc">
<p local-id=3D"592d6a44b60f">Agent detection and interactive/non-interactiv=
e selection logic.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f04a17b473d5">
<p local-id=3D"6f2c39549e75">Per-agent hook installation invocation and per=
-run summary output.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ce054bf130a">
<p local-id=3D"ad5fe83cef16">Telemetry consent capture and persistence rule=
s.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21b151cb8893">
<p local-id=3D"ca9e9253780a">Error and cancellation behaviour.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"894d7919b0a1" id=3D"bitloopsinit-Outofscope">Out of scope</=
h3>
<ul local-id=3D"464e2bd0009c">
<li local-id=3D"c48935cafe7d">
<p local-id=3D"2a851e93f375"><code>bitloops enable</code>/<code>disable</co=
de> behaviour (except helper calls used by <code>init</code>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4c4b0a61a4dd">
<p local-id=3D"f017f8e39b3c">Runtime processing of hook events after instal=
lation.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1962f905bd03">
<p local-id=3D"8bc10f51afc1">Uninstall behaviour.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1c288c1746b9">
<p local-id=3D"ee71abd1bf7d">Remote service APIs.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"583d05b5f902">
<h2 local-id=3D"526bee18a1cb" id=3D"bitloopsinit-4.Assumptions&amp;constrai=
nts">4. Assumptions &amp; constraints</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"af62ff07671a">
<li local-id=3D"5b47504b3787">
<p local-id=3D"b8157d491051">Command must run inside a Git repository (<cod=
e>find_repo_root</code> searches for <code>.git</code>, else errors).</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"492c4e5d4f96">
<p local-id=3D"1fd5da4deecf">Interactive agent picker requires terminal cap=
ability (<code>stdin/stdout</code> terminal or <code>/dev/tty</code>) and u=
ses <code>stty</code> raw mode.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"982805df4be0">
<p local-id=3D"5c31e5b74acb">Supported agent set is fixed in code: <code>cl=
aude-code</code>, <code>codex</code>, <code>cursor</code>, <code>gemini-cli=
</code>, <code>opencode</code>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1659fba6e7f8">
<p local-id=3D"daf20e7f8a86"><code>local_dev</code> settings flag controls =
command prefix for some generated hooks/plugins.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"815c395637d3">
<p local-id=3D"3de2fe846a84">Telemetry setting is persisted to <code>.bitlo=
