<hr local-id=3D"6ab72824791e">
<h2 local-id=3D"9c6b638ed866" id=3D"bitloopsinit-5.Userstories">5. User sto=
ries</h2>
<p local-id=3D"985afcad1d0d"><strong>US1 - Explicit agent initialisation</s=
trong> <br>
As a developer <br>
I want to run <code>bitloops init --agent &lt;name&gt;</code> <br>
So that only that agent=E2=80=99s integration is installed.</p>
<p local-id=3D"80589ceffe02"><strong>US2 - Interactive multi-agent initiali=
sation</strong> <br>
As a developer using multiple agents <br>
I want to select agents interactively <br>
So that one command initialises all required integrations.</p>
<p local-id=3D"95c1f097fb09"><strong>US3 - Non-interactive fallback behavio=
ur</strong> <br>
As a CI/script user <br>
I want deterministic non-interactive defaults <br>
So that init can run without prompts.</p>
<p local-id=3D"158f8d9a6756"><strong>US4 - Telemetry consent capture</stron=
g> <br>
As a user <br>
I want clear telemetry consent behaviour <br>
So that my preference is respected and persisted.</p>
