<hr local-id=3D"738e2d1d47e8">
<h2 local-id=3D"10cc35c026ac" id=3D"bitloopsinit-11.Businessrules">11. Busi=
ness rules</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6478c002890d">
<li local-id=3D"01a19ac876cd">
<p local-id=3D"c6ecc3f6f6d9">Command must resolve Git repo root before proc=
eeding.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f49392680726">
<p local-id=3D"481706ed7cb6"><code>--agent</code> path bypasses detection a=
nd interactive picker.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"85ddfa1554bd">
<p local-id=3D"bd8143a4141e">Agent detection is directory-based (<code>.cla=
ude</code>, <code>.codex</code>, <code>.cursor</code>, <code>.gemini</code>=
, <code>.opencode</code>).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8eaa8987832e">
<p local-id=3D"e310ad6b3906">Non-interactive fallback order: detected agent=
s, else installed agents, else default <code>claude-code</code>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"573819dcd8a0">
<p local-id=3D"3167885ade37">Interactive defaults order: installed agents, =
else detected agents, else default <code>claude-code</code>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c92f48261d2b">
<p local-id=3D"a9e549bd35b5">Selected agents are validated against availabl=
e set and de-duplicated.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b908d4357917">
<p local-id=3D"3c52674a4c56">Per-agent install is executed sequentially; to=
tal installed count is aggregated.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3ed4e91d1aa2">
<p local-id=3D"3784797944cf"><code>local_dev</code> settings value changes =
generated command prefix for compatible installers.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94d7f399c84c">
<p local-id=3D"7814730eac6f"><code>--telemetry=3Dfalse</code> always persis=
ts telemetry opt-out.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5f52b125f6b">
<p local-id=3D"3fb639527bdc"><code>BITLOOPS_TELEMETRY_OPTOUT</code> (non-em=
pty) always persists telemetry opt-out.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfc90b9cbec3">
<p local-id=3D"2f76c87250df">Existing telemetry setting is not re-prompted;=
 prompt only occurs when unset + interactive + no explicit <code>--agent</c=
ode>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b668a22fca35">
<p local-id=3D"90eaacb8d9b6">Init always prints a final summary block on su=
ccess.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"ffc7920784b0">
<h2 local-id=3D"af01fa829040" id=3D"bitloopsinit-12.Permissions&amp;roles">=
12. Permissions &amp; roles</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"3492ec13e96b">
<li local-id=3D"67c89500c1da">
