<li local-id=3D"51b55073dc30">
<p local-id=3D"4adfa0b36185">Operates with current local user permissions.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d28e9673bbb">
<p local-id=3D"459bf0673680">Requires write access to repository files for =
selected agent config paths and settings file.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e5f1d3f5be8">
<p local-id=3D"7116862e831d">No privileged operations or remote authenticat=
ion required for init itself.</p></li>
</ul>
