li>
<li local-id=3D"76f74f1edcee">
<p local-id=3D"5cf72f0d8127">Need to add better config options for the diff=
erent Stores. The default preselected could be at the user home folder and =
we could change it for the specific project if we want by including a confi=
g file with relevant entries at the project level. In --non-interactive mod=
